name: Goblin Head
description:
You're walking with your twin brother, when all of a sudden a voice talks to you. It's in your head, but you already know that, it's Her, the goddess that owns your soul, the goddess you don't believe in but still has power over you.

-This game has 5 endings. 

-If you pay $2 or more you get the android version!

You might need to enable a few cookies for the game to work properly.
